title: Cheap labs Design
descriptionMarkdown: Just it! A cheap lab design using only fast inserters and medium poles. > Just take 3 belts in the first lab below and connect it with inserters, or just put the sciences, and when you research the inserters will pass the sciences to the other labs, The order doesn't matter. Put sciences in each side of the belt. Space science doesn't need, that's why the Requester chest is there. This design is more for mid-late game than early-game. Just in case of that replace the medium poles with small ones, although you have to put more, and ignore the Requester chest. It's expandable, but will consume more sciences and then you'll need stack inserters just in the first lab, and express belts. Have fun!
